{"word":"συμπροθυμέομαι","slug":"συμπροθυμέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμπροθυμέομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to have equal desire with, share in eagerness with</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to join zealously in promoting</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> rei, <i>to take zealous part in</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to share in the desire that . .</i> , <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}